        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Insurance Not Covering 2 Years</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">Your policy must cover the full visa duration (up to 2 years). Monthly nomad insurance that can be cancelled won't work—you need proof of committed coverage.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Missing the 15-Day Cédula Deadline</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">You must apply for your Cédula de Extranjería within 15 days of arrival. Miss this and you'll face fines and complications.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Wrong Photo Format</h3>
